    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the lean pork mince has started to brown, add your <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> and <strong>remaining Marmite </strong>to the pan and cook for 1 min further or until caramelised</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
