        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the lean pork has caramelised (no pink meat!), add your <strong>udon noodles </strong>and <strong>spinach</strong> to the pan with 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]<strong> </span>water</strong> and cook, covered, for 2 min until the spinach has started to wilt</p><p>Tip: Gently separate the noodles with a fork!</p>",
